Dialogue: 4,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.14,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kazuya!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:25.81,0:03:26.93,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kazuya!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.72,Italics,,0,0,0,,Levante-se! Kazuya!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:31.98,0:03:37.98,Italics,,0,0,0,,Um verdadeiro homem japonês deve ser\N forte para proteger os mais fracos!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:38.57,0:03:40.86,Italics,,0,0,0,,Você é o terceiro filho de um soldado imperial!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:40.86,0:03:41.86,Italics,,0,0,0,,Acorde! Kazuya!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.74,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kazuya!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.28,Italics,,0,0,0,,Kazuya!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, você.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:47.16,0:03:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Estudante muito petulante.
Dialogue: 4,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Acorde!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:53.87,0:03:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Você não precisa me dizer, estou levantando!
Dialogue: 4,0:03:57.50,0:03:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:00.05,0:04:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Onde estamos?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:01.80,0:04:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Parece que a comida estava drogada.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:04.59,0:04:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Quando acordei já estava aqui no salão,\N pois fui trazida como todos os outros.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Onde?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:12.51,0:04:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Onde estamos?!
Dialogue: 4,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A porta não quer abrir!
Dialogue: 4,0:04:21.86,0:04:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,O que significa isso?!
Dialogue: 4,0:04:25.78,0:04:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 4,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas que coisa?!
Dialogue: 4,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kujou, há algo de errado aqui.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:33.58,0:04:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Antes havia nove pessoas na sala de jantar.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,E, incluindo nós dois, 11.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:40.50,0:04:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas agora há 12 pessoas aqui.
Dialogue: 4,0:04:43.69,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 4,0:04:45.13,0:04:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aumentou em uma pessoa.
